Samsung Galaxy S8





Sprint Flex 18 Mo. Lease

$000 Down /$3125 Month







2 for 1 with Sprint Lease
Lease a GS8 or GS8+, get a second GS8 lease on us. $31.25/mo. after $31.25/mo. service credit. Reqs. 2 new lines of service or 1 new line and 1 upgrade. For well-qualified customers with 18-mo. leases. Early termination results in remaining balance due. Credit applied within 2 invoices. GS8+: $4.17/mo. after $31.25/mo. service credit.


Shop now





