                Phone Replacement Programs


Insurance Claims

                
                If your phone has physical damage*, liquid damage, or was lost or stolen and you
                are enrolled in Total Equipment Protection (TEP) or Equipment Replacement Program (ERP)
                you may expedite the claim process by visiting
                www.phoneclaim.com
                to submit your claim request for a replacement phone.
                

                  * Physical damage includes, but not limited to, items such as cracked displays, broken flips, and damaged charging ports.
                






