ock Option Said to Emerge     6/2/2017   T-Mobile Tries Out Its Sprint Pitch on Wall Street as Talks Get Under Way     5/18/2017   T-Mobile Calls Sprint Most Logical Partner as Deal Talk Heats Up     5/12/2017   Sprint, SoftBank Said in Informal Deal Talks With T-Mobile    There are currently no news stories for this ticker. Please check back later.     7/21/2017   Twice the Price Store Announces Grand Opening in New York     7/20/2017   Sprint Expands in the Portland Metro with Nine New Retail Stores Creating 50 Jobs     7/20/2017   Sprint Expands in Washington with 12 New Retail Stores Creating More Than 80 Jobs     7/20/2017   Sprint Opens Five Stores in Indianapolis     7/19/2017   Sprint Brings Hundreds of Jobs to Central and North Florida     7/18/2017   Sprint Corporation Schedules Fiscal 2017 First Quarter Results Announcement     7/14/2017   Sprint Flex is The Best Way to Get the Latest Smartphone     7/13/2017   Award-Winning BlackBerry® KEYone Available At Sprint Beginning Tomorrow     7/6/2017   Sprint Gives Soccer Fanatics a Chance to Win During the 2017 Gold Cup     7/6/2017   Worldwide Smart Home M2M Market: Presence of Many Prominent Players Makes Competition Stiff, Finds TMR    There are currently no press releases for this ticker. Please check back later.      Profile   Sprint Corporation offers a comprehensive range of wireless and wireline communications products and services to consumers, businesses, government subscribers, and resellers. The Company develops, engineers, and deploys various technologies that include an all-digital global wireline network and a global Tier 1 Internet backbone.    Address  6200 Sprint ParkwayOverland Park, KS 66251United States   Phone  1-800-829-0965   Website   www.sprint.com     Executives Board Members    Tarek Robbiati  Chief Financial Officer    Raul Marcelo Claure  President/CEO    Nestor Cano  Chief Operating Officer    John Cb Saw  Chief Technology Officer    Roger Sole Rafols  Chief Marketing Officer    